what_we_did: Calculated risk for all options using Greeks

greek_explanations.delta: How much option price changes when stock moves $1
greek_explanations.theta: How much money we lose each day (time decay)
greek_explanations.gamma: How much delta speeds up or slows down
greek_explanations.vega: How much price changes if volatility changes
greek_explanations.implied_volatility: How jumpy people think the stock will be
